# AI Prompts Tracker

This file tracks all prompts used in the development of the Task Management Utility.

---

## PROMPT #1 - CODE TYPE

| Field    | Value        |
|----------|--------------|
| Type     | CODE         |
| Date     | 2026-02-13   |

### Prompt

> We are writing project in plain javascript, no fancy stuff.
> Keep css in separate file.
> Create file ai_prompts.txt and store all prompts in there, keep track if it is code, ask or other type of prompt.

### Objective

Build a browser-based task management utility.

### Requirements

- CRUD operations for tasks (stored in browser storage - localStorage or IndexedDB)
- Task properties: `id`, `title`, `description`, `status`, `priority`, `dueDate`, `tags[]`
- Commands: `add`, `list`, `update`, `delete`, `filter`, `search`
- Async operations with proper error handling
- Input validation

